- SLS_LOG_DS: A LogStore data source.

- SLS_METRIC_DS: A MetricStore data source.', example='SLS_LOG_DS'),
    }
  ](name='dsList', description='Applies to the SLS_MULTI_DS data source type.

A list of sub-data sources.'),
  instanceId?: string(name='instanceId', description='Applies to the PROMETHEUS_DS data source type.

The ID of the Prometheus instance.', example='rw-bbe8961b4a59be0'),
  namespace?: string(name='namespace', description='Applies to the ENTERPRISE_DS data source type.

The name of the Hybrid Cloud Monitoring metric repository.', example='aliyun-default'),
  regionId?: string(name='regionId', description='Applies to the APM_DS and PROMETHEUS_DS data source types.

The ID of the region where the data source is located.', example='cn-hangzhou'),
  tenantId?: string(name='tenantId'),
  type?: string(name='type', description='The data source type.

Valid values:

- PROMETHEUS_DS: A Prometheus data source.

- SLS_MULTI_DS: An SLS data source.

- APM_DS: An Application Monitoring data source.

- CMS_BASIC_DS: A basic Cloud Monitor data source.

- ENTERPRISE_DS: A Hybrid Cloud Monitoring data source.

This parameter is required.', example='PROMETHEUS_DS'),
}

