The query expression (PromQL).', example='sum(sum(max_over_time(kube_pod_status_phase{phase=~\\\\"Pending\\\\",job=\\\\"_kube-state-metrics\\\\"}[5m])) by (pod)) > 1000'),
  firstJoin?: AlertRuleSlsQueryJoin(name='firstJoin', description='Applicable query type: SLS_MULTI_QUERY.

